data.description: 2 or 3 bedrooms (2 BR suites w/full bath) 2.5 baths, covered rear patio, no other homes are located right behind you.  Built in 2022 with interior features that include;  open floor plan with 9' ceiling, master suite w/dual walk in closets and master bathroom, custom kitchen cabinets w/soft open and close feature, upgraded granite-quartz counter tops, and stainless appliance package, carpeting and vinyl plank flooring, full second bedroom suite and 3rd bedroom or office.  Exterior construction is vinyl, stone and brick w/over sized 2-car garage.  Natural gas heat, central AC, public water and sewer.  HOA fee is $81.00 per month and includes grass mowing and snow removal.
